8,"arabic":"٥٩","translation":"(৫৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":60,"arabic":"۞ ذَٰلِكَ وَمَنْ عَاقَبَ بِمِثْلِ مَا عُوقِبَ بِهِۦ ثُمَّ بُغِىَ عَلَيْهِ لَيَنصُرَنَّهُ ٱللَّهُ ۗ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ لَعَفُوٌّ غَفُورٌۭ","translation":"Thus shall it be. And as for him who responds to aggression only to the extent of the attack levelled against him, and is thereupon [again] treacherously attacked - God will most certainly succour him: for, behold, God is indeed an absolver of sins, much-forgiving.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2655.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":54300,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা (এদের পরিনতি)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54301,"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"আর যে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54302,"position":3,"arabic":"عَاقَبَ","translation":"প্রতিশোধ নিবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54303,"position":4,"arabic":"بِمِثْلِ","translation":"(তার) সমতুল্য","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54304,"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54305,"position":6,"arabic":"عُوقِبَ","translation":"নিপীড়ন করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54306,"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"প্রতি তার","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54307,"position":8,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"আবার","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54308,"position":9,"arabic":"بُغِىَ","translation":"বাড়াবাড়ি করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54309,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/022_060_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54310,"position":11,"arabic":"لَيَنصُرَنَّهُ","translation":"অবশ্যই তাকে সাহায্য করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/022